Context:
The Personal Support Worker Pathway to Practical Nursing (S119) program is offered at George Brown College. Interested individuals can learn more about the program by watching a previously recorded online information session. The session covers details about program content, further study options upon graduation, and college life.

Application deadlines, college news, upcoming events, tours, and other related information can be obtained by signing up. George Brown College can be reached via phone at 416-415-2000 or TTY at 1-877-515-5559, or by email at ask.george@georgebrown.ca.

The information contained in the website is subject to change without notice and should not be considered a representation, offer, or warranty. Students are responsible for verifying George Brown College fee requirements.
